summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 2861 for the improvement of the alley in Block Fourteen (14), Maynard's Addition to the City of Seattle, (being the Alley from Jackson Street to Main Street, between Second Avenue South and Third Avenue South) all in the City of Seattle, by planking the same, under Ordinance No. 34720, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
